{"tid":2037410,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"YouTube指武肺AI誤刪批評共產黨評論","createTime":"2020-05-27T03:26:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T06:04:42.000Z","uid":21470,"like":14,"dislike":281,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"6faef9b23984059cf2542562b17e3bef0c786af9","tid":2037410,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:26:44.000Z","msg":"YouTube指因糸統錯誤曾刪批評共產黨評論<br />\n27.05.2020 11:20<br />\n<br />\nYouTube證實曾經刪除批評中國共產黨的評論，解釋是由於過濾系統錯誤，正展開調查。近日有用戶反映，在影片下留言批評共產黨的字眼，包括「共匪」、「五毛」等，隨即被自動刪除。Youtube發聲明，否認是更改政策，指由於在新型冠狀病毒病大流行期間，較依賴自動過濾器，人工審核相對較少所致。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle搜尋引擎已於2010年撤出中國，旗下的YouTube亦不在中國營運。《彭博社》報道，包括中國在內的一些國家，雖然未使用YouTube，仍要求Google審查部份在境外播放的影片。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1291359&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1291359%26csid%3D261_341&d=y71HX3BFsGTccDILyV%2F8U0YD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=2238936f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1291359&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"2c056c32f4da3d627304fb023eaf4b1237e37bd0","tid":2037410,"uid":301952,"like":148,"dislike":0,"score":148,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:28:10.000Z","msg":"兜咩丫<br />\n索性認奶共，好過兩面唔係人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e1e2c3b74de65126130aac2960ae429046f16dd","tid":2037410,"uid":121146,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:28:44.000Z","msg":"諗起前幾年成班傻西係度奶Google就好笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44aa326e6e320d389f50a77009cf05537afc0808","tid":2037410,"uid":31237,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T03:29:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">誤</span>"},{"pid":"97a34ea0d65c1bb25659f4fb4ff55749ea24eff4","tid":2037410,"uid":228894,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T0